Module de.sft.dl
Package de.s42.dl.parser.expression

Class DLHrfExpressionParser

java.lang.Object
de.s42.dl.parser.expression.DLHrfExpressionParser
public final class DLHrfExpressionParser extends Object
Handles expressions in DL. This is just a reference implementation. In case expressions will be part of the DL spec this has to be optimized. See https://github.com/studio42gmbh/dl/issues/20
Author:
Benjamin Schiller
